description: Here's what you might have missed Wednesday on CNN
title: Quickly catch up on the day's news
title_page: News today: Symptoms, small businesses, stimulus checks, face masks - CNN
maintext:
(CNN) Here's what you might have missed Wednesday on CNN:
-- New estimates show 25% to 50% of coronavirus carriers don't even have symptoms and can infect others blindly , fueling the spread of the virus. In fact, lab tests in Iceland suggest 50% of coronavirus cases exhibit no symptoms.
-- On just one block in America, six businesses are on the brink of disaster. These are their stories.
-- Meanwhile, some business are seeing a huge surge in sales as Americans everywhere change their daily habits.
-- Stimulus cash is coming to everyday Americans. Here are answers to your questions about when you will get it and how it will arrive.
-- Andrew Jack, a British actor and dialect coach who had roles in "Star Wars" movies, has died aged 76 after contracting Covid-19.
